transformers_text:
Jacob Romero Gibson (born July 11, 1996) is an American actor. He is known for playing the role of Usopp in the Netflix series One Piece (2023).

From 2019 to 2020, he played the role of AJ Delajae in a total of 15 episodes of the television series Greenleaf . [ 1 ] [ 2 ]

Beginning in 2023, he played the role of Usopp in the Netflix series One Piece , based on the manga of the same name . [ 3 ] [ 4 ]
